Account Deletion Instructions ‚Äì Blup! Medical
If you wish to delete your Blup! Medical account, you may do so at any time by sending a request to our support team. Please note that account deletion is a manual process to ensure the security and privacy of your data.

üì© To request deletion:
Send an email to support@blupmedical.com

Use the subject line: Account Deletion Request

Include the following details in the body of the email:

Your full name

The email address associated with your Blup! Medical account

(Optional) Reason for deleting the account

Once we receive your request, we will:

Verify your identity for security purposes.

Process your deletion within 7 business days.

Permanently remove your data from our active systems, unless retention is required by law (e.g., medical or legal regulations).

If you have any questions or concerns about this process, feel free to contact us at the same email address.

